    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i've heard some people say that raising the wage is actually good because it puts more money in people's pockets so they spend more in the local economy, which helps businesses. is that actually a real thing that happens in small towns, or is that just something people say to make it sound better?",
