    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds good in theory but sounds a bit optimistic for someone like me. i don't know if my customers will actually spend more if my prices have to go up to cover the wages. wouldn't the higher costs for the business usually just cancel out the extra money people have? it seems like the people pushing for these hikes tend to ignore the actual math that small business owners have to deal with every day.",
